Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:09.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.90,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixteen Years Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name will be Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's name him Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a wonderful name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason's obvious, isn't it, Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want him to grow up strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he can run like the gale \N(hayate) away from bill collectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that a {\i1}fantastic{\i0} name!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is, right? I'm a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when we have to \Nabandon our child to go on the run,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have nothing to worry about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, you really are something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:50.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus named Hayate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:53.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the boy's destiny was thrust \Nupon him from the day he was born
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:56.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to become absolutely perfect at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:58.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know, ladies and gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:03.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That a humongous mansion like \Nthis exists somewhere in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss's name is Nagi Sanzenin. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:10.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Her butler's name is Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They are both a bit clueless
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:14.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and both have a bit of the \Nwrong idea about each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.79,0:01:19.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but they share the immensely strong, \Nloving bond between servant and mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.74,0:01:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of America cried!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make ya laugh 3 times in 5 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already, no hope for the Academy Award!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:28.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\N I don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai! \NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:36.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\N The future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:41.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Honne o misecha make datoka \NStuff like, showing your true feelings means defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:46.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentaku hajiku jinsei datoka\N Or a life tapping away at a calculator
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:51.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro o itsuwaru kurai nara\N Rather than be false to myself like that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:57.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichiten-battou baka-shoujiki mo kuuzen-zetsugo! \NI'll struggle to be uniquely naive and honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:02.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Komatta kao o mireba ki-ni-naru shi\N If I see a troubled look, I'll be concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:07.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Jinsei isogu riyuu mo betsuni nai shi \NAnd it's not like I've got a reason to hurry through life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:13.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu wa kimi ni azukeyou \NI'll entrust you with the treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:19.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin yori-michi datte tsukiau yo! \NI'll even keep you company on your free-ranging detours
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:22.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rakkii-sugiru tenkai \NA development that's way too lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:25.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotae wa mayowanai \NI won't hesitate to give my answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kantan sa! Subete wa kimi no tame ni \NIt's easy! It's all for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuuhyou wa ki-ni-shinai \NI won't worry about the rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:36.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rettou-kan ni doujinai!\N I won't let a sense of inferiority get to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:41.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakedasu shunkan wa ima koko ni aru \NThe moment to start running is right here, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a Dog, a Mouse, and a Bulldog
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? \NIs it not a fabulous portrait?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's apparently a gift of sorts, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much do you \Nthink this is valued at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so... Open the price!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ones, tens, hundreds, thousands, \Nten thousands, hundred thousands,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,millions, ten millions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two hundred million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cheaper than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have brought the milk tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, well, in 10 years, \Nmy autographed illustrations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will probably be worth 100 times \Nmore than this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you still do not understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what true quality is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know that this august painting \Nis worth even more
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than your debt, which you'll spend \Nthe rest of your life repaying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We actually received word just earlier \Nthat this painting appears to be a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:12.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CRUSHED
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, it's been a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd go be a Giant \Nof Art in the storehouse or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But anyway, you have \Na brilliantly discerning eye, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that painting was fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from back when I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but well, I used to help with my \Nfather's business and sell art.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so your father was an art dealer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Truly, you have a sharp eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, we would first \Nshow them the real painting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when the customer had made a purchase,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would hand it over to me right \Nin front of the customer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to avoid suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy will package it up for you then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please wait one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:05:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were dealing with valuables, \Nso the customers are also wary, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seemed to lower their guard, \Nknowing I was a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I would make it look like \NI was packaging up the real thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I would switch it with a fake \Nthat was hidden behind the real one
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sell the customer that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a crime, no two ways about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was little, so I didn't \Nknow it was a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was when my father drummed into me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how to instantly recognize fakes \Nfor all kinds of paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much worthless information \Ndid you have drummed into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:31.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate Ayasaki, protagonist of this manga \Nand occasionally its heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not out to destroy the Andro Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:35.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but he possesses an invulnerable body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The author loved the World \NMasterpiece Theater too much
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and before he realized it, he had \Ncreated an utterly unfortunate boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been reading from, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, something's been bothering me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm reading the original manga \Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:57.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. I wish you \Nwouldn't rob me of my job...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think Hayate's abilities \Nare amazing, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Too{\i0} amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's deft, but he also \Nhas great physical strength
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he accomplishes all \Ntasks perfectly and swiftly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, on to the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of which, he's got \Nincomprehensible special powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making him too good to be \Nthe protagonist of a romantic comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we do occasionally get \Nthe shoehorned battles, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, here's a question I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he have any weaknesses or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weaknesses! You know, weaknesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon has mice, Oba-Q has dogs, \Nand Goku has his tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the heroes of manga and anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they tend to come with \Nweaknesses by default, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Hayate's amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's got a bit of this aura \Nthat makes you want to be mean to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I won't deny it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As someone who shares Robocon's \Nweakness, you agree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have \Nanything to do with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really! I wish you wouldn't \Nremind me of such unpleasantness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I think Hayate needs a weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hinomaru Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:24.96,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Ru Ma No Hi{right to left}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared items that could \Npossibly be weaknesses for Hayate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the form of "Hinomaru" boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, then I'll take the "ma" from "Hinomaru".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Open the box!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that creepy thing away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you shouldn't have \Nprepared it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it really was stupid of us \Nto rely on Saito the announcer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, "us"? It's not like I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we'll just have to discover \Nhis weaknesses through observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that's correct, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally overcome my math weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of Hayate's rare \Nweaknesses has been overcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't think that's \Nnecessarily a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have any other weaknesses \Nor things he doesn't like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to observe carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss won't eat sardines like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll mince it up a bit and get rid \Nof the fishiness with ginger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she doesn't like carrots \Nor green peppers, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, she absolutely won't eat spicy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and she doesn't like \Nchicken skin, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's observed you carefully \Non your weaknesses and dislikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, it's because she's \Nso picky that her growth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! Hayate, you're really... I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have no choice but to go after him \Nwith standard weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? This'll scare him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's just scary in all sorts of ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gets scared when a ghost shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:59.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that more like your own weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Now, I just have to wait \Nuntil night to catch Hayate sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not see the need to wait until night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, if you just darken \Nthe room like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-Nah, Maria, i-isn't it still too early?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll have to go to these lengths,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or he won't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be {\i1}that{\i0} scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya got a long way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fermented soybeans, red miso soup, \Nsavory monja pancakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's weaknesses, \NI'll give ya a run for yer money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you pop out from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The butler-in-debt's weakness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys like him sometimes have \Nthe most unexpected weaknesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unexpected?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrifyin' invaders who forced humanity \Nto the brink of extinction...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But their sinister plot's \Ndestroyed by microorganisms!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the weakness of aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, I cannot leave this to Saku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could come up with a good idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My idea is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can simply ask him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't thought of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is it that you \Nare afraid of, my dear Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This is about where \NI'd be afraid of a cup of tea."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,For those of you who don't get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,please listen to the traditional rakugo \Nstory called "Scared of Manju Sweets".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, an Edo Era punchline?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of Dom Pérignon! \NI'm scared of Dom Pérignon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the feeling something just went by...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Nwhat's yer weakness, Isumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wonderin' if even the supreme \NGhost Sweeper's afraid of somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I am afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid of caterpillars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caterpillars?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? That's an awfully \Nnormal thing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a body length of 180 meters \Nand weighing 20,000 tons,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is the guardian deity of Infant Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It spun a giant cocoon on Tokyo Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even an atomic heat ray \Nattack had no effect on it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and once it became an imago,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is said to have devastated \Na certain country...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, that's no caterpillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If that'll be all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you sleep.\N({\u1}Ne{\u0}kasanai {\u1}yo{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With pleasure.\N({\u1}Yo{\u0}rokon{\u1}de{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate you treating us \Nto lunch as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:11.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,She certainly left them neatly uneaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:17.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably thought you \Ntook advantage of my weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but it won't be so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:23.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I'll be sure to uncover your weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you still haven't given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once everything's cleaned up, \Nwould it be all right if I took a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, I won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing much. I just thought \NI'd get back to my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the finals are coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must work hard to advance \Nto the next grade with you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-With me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two better not interfere \Nwith Hayate's studies, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By no means are you to get any silly ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,such as being hell-bent \Non discovering his weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall be careful, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, I have the math \Nproblems from last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to look \Nat them for reference?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I would love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is math, and yet, \Nthe problems aren't in Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's in German.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! German?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Germany is the land of sausages!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they've got other \Nthings like beer, too, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that! This is way \Nbeyond the level of "hard"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello there, Wataru. Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting a great \Nnumber of guests today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you suddenly \Nstorming in here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I here for? \NI mean, what's up with this exam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Hakuou {\i1}is{\i0} \Na prestigious school, after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's only natural that it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's hard and then there's this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! There's \Nno way we can read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can't read that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:58.94,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi Saginomiya: 4 Languages
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.10,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria: 13 Languages
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:01.27,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi Sanzenin: 8 Languages
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.57,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru Tachibana: 2 Languages
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you skipped grades \Nand you can't even read German?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got my hands full with just English!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you could choose to have problems \Nin English as well on the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, even English is kind of iffy for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.42,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate Ayasaki: 1.5 Languages
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just for my own reference,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what will happen \Nif I should fail or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't fall silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goin' to a prestigious \Nschool sure sounds tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I'm goin' to a normal school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:37.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Saku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, guess playtime's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya guys study hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Isumi, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, 'cause Wataru won't be able to \Nfocus on his studies with ya around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why would Wataru have problems...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saku, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Nagi, we'll leave the rest to ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's go, Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no helping it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:12.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, \Nover at a normal high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with this quiz score?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:19.31,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumu Nishizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be kind of bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with talk of love and romance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:27.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the realities of high school life are harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.78,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Newest Edition\NUnderstandable German
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, because there's a limit to how much \Nyou can study on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd go look after my \Nless accomplished little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there really \Nare limits on your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unlike you, he's not the sort \Nwho can do it just by working at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um... Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to go \Ntutor Wataru over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not tolerate a Sanzenin \Nbutler getting a failing grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do now, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tutor me, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! You better be \Nat least a little grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am. Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel bad for Saku \Nif you flunked or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had no idea that both Wataru \Nand Isumi had skipped grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \NI guess we never mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without friends, Nagi would probably \Ncompletely stop going to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we had them skip grades with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their grades were good, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind you, it was originally supposed to be \NIsumi and Sakuya who went with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, with Wataru, skipping \Ngrades was a pretty big stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was a reason Wataru \Ndesperately wanted to go to Hakuou
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and only 3 slots available \Nfor skipping grades, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.65,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(30,15)\an7}Mr. Wataru Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.65,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(30,40)\an7} Enrollment Paperwork \NHakuou Academy Entrance Exam Center
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi tutored him at that time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if the Small Beauties \Nof Infant Island become lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the entire world will surely fall \Ninto a panic once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, enough 'bout that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how's school these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it still fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but Nagi does not come \Nto school much, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Wataru's 'bout \Nthe only playmate you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not entirely true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only say hello to Wataru \Nevery one in a while anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought maybe they \Nwere slowly gettin' somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened to King Ghidorah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Um, King Ghidorah was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is a little worrisome, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean the Miss and Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may still be children,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for a young man and a young \Nwoman to be alone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we should figure out a nice timing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to bring them coffee or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking too much about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if we start talking \Nabout a young man
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a young woman being alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we are also...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:06.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The cliché romantic comedy mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we bring them coffee, after all? \NFinding a nice timing for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Perhaps we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel bad that you're \Nalways tutoring me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this creepy gracious attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You idiot! I'm always gracious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be more endearing \Nif you were always this gracious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have brought you coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you holding hands \Nwhile you're studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this wrong, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This just sort of happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just sort of happened... \Nand you were trying to do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Hayate! \NThis is a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I wouldn't even {\i1}want{\i0} \Nto do anything to Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:19:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost while I was \Nchasing after Sakuya and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You got it all wrong, Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-This is... You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just kidding. I was trying to go \Nfor a joke or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, so it was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ya have any desire \Nto make progress here?! Ya wuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, going to the same \Nschool has been meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can rest easy and go study with Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You can rest easy and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second. What did \Nyou say you're going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, as I said, go study with Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go study with Maria, just the two of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do such a thing \Nbehind my back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you! This is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, what are you so angry about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear your excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:16.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it seems not \Nunderstanding a girl's feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:19.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,is Hayate's greatest weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:23.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, next time, even \NHollywood films will be shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:25.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll fight against a luxury \Npassenger liner, terrorists,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and man-eating sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to "go Isumi" on jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that should've been \N"go easy"! Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love telling jokes, \Ndon't you, Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they are not very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as a creature, I think \Nhe might be kind of funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll hafta give him some lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:22:05.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaretai fureraretetai\NI want to be loved, to feel that touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:10.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Motomeru bakari no kimochi wa\NThe sense of continually seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:14.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibi o kumoraseteta\NUsed to darken my days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:22.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ni deau sono hi made wa\NUntil the day I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:31.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Namae yonde sora ni hibiku-youni\NCall my name so it echoes to the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:41.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi-michi mo kitto futari nara\NEven lost, with the two of us, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:47.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunaida te to te hanasanai\NI won't let go of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:50.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoritainda\NI want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:56.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Saa ikou bokura wa\NCome on, let's go, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:23:08.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima o mitsumete aruki-hajimeru\N...look at the present and start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:27.42,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,The Katsura Sisters'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:27.42,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(214.222,282)} Lettering by Hitomi Nabatame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Katsura sisters'...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:29.09,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boom! It's Yukiji Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boom! I am Hinagiku Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the much talked-about pair \Nof pretty girls, the Katsura sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you sure about this, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going along with this because you say
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.54,0:23:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is your moment in the spotlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is really embarrassing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.59,0:23:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, your enthusiasm is lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we practiced this so many \Ntimes yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.80,0:23:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this song sells, I can say goodbye \Nto my hard life of poverty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.76,0:23:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to drink all \Nthe Dom Pérignon I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, see you again next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:57.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So that's what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:23:59.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I haven't won Hayate over...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:24:18.43,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:00.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing \Nwhen it comes to romance...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:02.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...is giving the cold shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:05.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want a situation where Hayate \Nwill rely on me more somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.83,0:24:08.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, you've been invited on \Nan ocean voyage on Sakuya's yacht.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.02,0:24:12.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "The Poseidon \NAdvance Generator Gavas"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.86,0:24:15.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,But this ship's pretty well-built.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.33,0:24:16.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya think so? That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:20.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You can give me the cold shoulder \Nall you want! I'm not falling for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.43,0:24:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Poseidon Advance Generator Gavas
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.14,0:24:23.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just In to "Hayate the Combat \NButler" again next time!
